=== CATEGORIES ===\
\
Primary Key: CategoryID\
Parent Tables: None\
What does a record represent: One product category like Beverages or Dairy\
Valuable columns: CategoryID, CategoryName, Description\
Calculations possible: Count products per category\
\
\
=== CUSTOMERS ===\
Primary Key: CustomerID\
Parent Tables: None\
What does a record represent: One customer company \
that buys products from Northwind Traders\
Valuable columns: CustomerID, CompanyName, \
City, Country, ContactName\
Calculations possible: Count orders per customer,\
total revenue per customer, customers by country\
\
